snippet.title: Pahile Pahil Chhathi Maiya | Sharda Sinha | Chhath Song
snippet.description:
Dedicated to the next generation of devotees of Sun God by one and only Sharda sinha. The song conveys the simplistic and earthy connection of chhat - aastha ka mahaparv and acknowledges the version 2.0 of Chhat festival. The song symbolises that purity and faith of this grand festival can be beautifully carried forward by new people and generations.
Its a pleasure for Worldwide Records to be associated with the song by Sharda Sinha ji  on the auspicious occasion of Chhat pooja
Thanks to the efforts of Anshuman Sinha for bringing a Sharda Sinha ji oon This Platform and among the new generation.
